    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>The collection contains a list of communicants, 1893-1894,
         1897-1898, 1899, 1901, 1902, 1903, 1905 and index, vestry
         records, 1838-1933, 1940-1949, 1950-1970, marriage register,
         1932-1950, church service registers, 1949-1962, parish
         registers, 1836-1950, minutes and correspondence about St.
         Anne's school, 1903-1953, register of church services,
         1941-1949, and treasurer's records, 1930-1963.</p>
    </scopecontent>
